Interaction Cat Paw Dog Toy for Medium and Large Dogs: This dog toy is an ideal interactive dog toy that makes companionship more interesting. Interacting with dogs through this large-sized dog interactive toy will increase the fun between dogs and make time for dogs alone become fun. This toy will be the best gift for medium-sized dogs or large aggressive chewing dogs.
